{"key":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01|1Th|5","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Th","chapter":5,"textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024","parserRevision":"v11","verses":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Th:5:1","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Th","bookOrder":51,"chapter":5,"verse":1,"text":"About the times and the seasons: Brothers and sisters, you do not need anything to be written to you.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Th:5:2","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Th","bookOrder":51,"chapter":5,"verse":2,"text":"For you yourselves know very well that the day of the Lord will come just like a thief in the night.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Th:5:3","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Th","bookOrder":51,"chapter":5,"verse":3,"text":"When they say, “Peace and security,” then sudden destruction will come upon them, like labor pains on a pregnant woman, and they will not escape.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Th:5:4","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Th","bookOrder":51,"chapter":5,"verse":4,"text":"But you, brothers and sisters, are not in the dark, for this day to surprise you like a thief.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Th:5:5","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Th","bookOrder":51,"chapter":5,"verse":5,"text":"For you are all children of light and children of the day. We do not belong to the night or the darkness.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Th:5:6","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Th","bookOrder":51,"chapter":5,"verse":6,"text":"So then, let us not sleep, like the rest, but let us stay awake and be self-controlled.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Th:5:7","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Th","bookOrder":51,"chapter":5,"verse":7,"text":"For those who sleep, sleep at night, and those who get drunk, get drunk at night.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Th:5:8","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Th","bookOrder":51,"chapter":5,"verse":8,"text":"But since we belong to the day, let us be self-controlled and put on the armor of faith and love, and a helmet of the hope of salvation.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Th:5:9","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Th","bookOrder":51,"chapter":5,"verse":9,"text":"For God did not appoint us to wrath, but to obtain salvation through our Lord Jesus Christ,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Th:5:10","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Th","bookOrder":51,"chapter":5,"verse":10,"text":"who died for us, so that whether we are awake or asleep, we may live together with him.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Th:5:11","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Th","bookOrder":51,"chapter":5,"verse":11,"text":"Therefore encourage one another and build each other up as you are already doing.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Th:5:12","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Th","bookOrder":51,"chapter":5,"verse":12,"text":"Now we ask you, brothers and sisters, to give recognition to those who labor among you and lead you in the Lord and admonish you,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Th:5:13","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Th","bookOrder":51,"chapter":5,"verse":13,"text":"and to regard them very highly in love because of their work. Be at peace among yourselves.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Th:5:14","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Th","bookOrder":51,"chapter":5,"verse":14,"text":"And we exhort you, brothers and sisters: warn those who are idle, comfort the discouraged, help the weak, be patient with everyone.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Th:5:15","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Th","bookOrder":51,"chapter":5,"verse":15,"text":"See to it that no one repays evil for evil to anyone, but always pursue what is good for one another and for all.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Th:5:16","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Th","bookOrder":51,"chapter":5,"verse":16,"text":"Rejoice always,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Th:5:17","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Th","bookOrder":51,"chapter":5,"verse":17,"text":"pray constantly,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Th:5:18","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Th","bookOrder":51,"chapter":5,"verse":18,"text":"give thanks in everything; for this is God’s will for you in Christ Jesus.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Th:5:19","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Th","bookOrder":51,"chapter":5,"verse":19,"text":"Don’t stifle the Spirit.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Th:5:20","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Th","bookOrder":51,"chapter":5,"verse":20,"text":"Don’t despise prophecies,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Th:5:21","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Th","bookOrder":51,"chapter":5,"verse":21,"text":"but test all things. Hold on to what is good.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Th:5:22","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Th","bookOrder":51,"chapter":5,"verse":22,"text":"Stay away from every kind of evil.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Th:5:23","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Th","bookOrder":51,"chapter":5,"verse":23,"text":"Now may the God of peace himself sanctify you completely. And may your whole spirit, soul, and body be kept sound and blameless at the coming of our Lord Jesus Christ.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Th:5:24","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Th","bookOrder":51,"chapter":5,"verse":24,"text":"He who calls you is faithful; he will do it.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Th:5:25","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Th","bookOrder":51,"chapter":5,"verse":25,"text":"Brothers and sisters, pray for us also.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Th:5:26","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Th","bookOrder":51,"chapter":5,"verse":26,"text":"Greet all the brothers and sisters with a holy kiss.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Th:5:27","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Th","bookOrder":51,"chapter":5,"verse":27,"text":"I charge you by the Lord that this letter be read to all the brothers and sisters.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Th:5:28","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Th","bookOrder":51,"chapter":5,"verse":28,"text":"The grace of our Lord Jesus Christ be with you.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"}],"layout":{"bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Th","chapter":5,"paragraphStarts":[1,12,23],"headings":[{"beforeVerse":1,"text":"The Day of the Lord"},{"beforeVerse":12,"text":"Exhortations and Blessings"}],"poetryBlocks":[],"studyByVerse":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Th:5:1","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"About the times and the seasons: "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dn 2:21","book":"Dan","chapter":2,"verse":21,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 1:7","book":"Act","chapter":1,"verse":7,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" Brothers and sisters, you do not need anything to be written to you. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Dn 2:21","book":"Dan","chapter":2,"vers